title: 01/21: TEN and GB Offseason Questions; Best Spot to Draft In; Early Super Bowl Preview! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
The Super Bowl is set and we'll give you our initial picks with plenty of time to change our minds! What will be the difference in the big game? Then we look back at the weekend with players who impressed us (10:30) and players who did not impress us (22:22). Can Raheem Mostert be a feature back in the SF offense? Does that offense make George Kittle risky in 2020? We also discuss DFS from the weekend (30:50) ... News and notes (34:10) including Jason Garrett's track record as a play caller, plus Kellen Moore and Philip Rivers notes. And we answer questions about TEN and GB (40:40). Is Ryan Tannehill good? Can Aaron Rodgers be elite again? Can Aaron Jones be elite again? Oh, and let's discuss why Derrick Henry could be a bust ... We tell you which draft slots had the highest championship percentages and what it means for 2020 (50:30) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
